    <paragraphs>
      <title>Learning Outcomes</title>

      <p>
        By the end of this course, you should be able to:
        <ol>
          <li> 
            <p> 	Apply techniques from multivariable analysis to construct 
              mathematical models and obtain results,
            </p>
          </li>

          <li>
            <p> Construct series representations of functions and use them to 
              solve applied problems,
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p> Investigate partial differential equations and their solutions.
              
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </p>
